dct_title_s: The sources of the Brahmaputra, Sutlej, and Indus : based upon original obsevations by Dr. Sven Hedin and incorporating the surveys of the previous travellers, especially those of Major Ryden \ by Dr. Sven Hedin ; compiled by Lieutenant C. J. Otto Kjellström.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures and spot heights. Depth shown by soundings. Map show with red lines the routes travelled by explorers. Includes index in companion volume. Companion volume can be requested form ReCap Remote Storage: Call number DS785 .H52 1909
